title: A PIECE Of PIE, On Me
body_text: The East Coast Dodgeball World will be treated to a Turkey Day celebration of its own when ECD's most recognized female star collides with the biggest female weapon for the very first time ever. And in the spirit of the holiday, one will be served a great big piece of that delicious cream pie. It's DiBuccio-Kerr on 11 22.
